# Kotlin Coroutines Masterclass

[![Kotlin Version](https://img.shields.io/badge/Kotlin-1.9.0-blue.svg)](https://kotlinlang.org/)
[![Coroutines Version](https://img.shields.io/badge/Coroutines-1.7.3-orange.svg)](https://github.com/Kotlin/kotlinx.coroutines)

A practical guide to mastering Kotlin Coroutines with real-world examples. Learn asynchronous programming concepts through hands-on exercises specifically designed for Android developers.

## Features
- Basic to advanced coroutine concepts
- Practical examples with detailed explanations
- Best practices for Android development
- Common use cases and patterns
- Performance optimization tips

## What's Inside
- Basic coroutine launching
- Async/Await patterns
- Coroutine scopes and contexts
- Error handling strategies
- Flow API examples
- Channel communication
- Android-specific implementations

## Prerequisites
- Basic knowledge of Kotlin
- Android Studio (latest version)
- Kotlin plugin installed

## Getting Started
1. Clone this repository
```bash
git clone https://github.com/<your-username>/kotlin-coroutines-masterclass.git
